EXOBIUS 0 - Instructions
========================

Installation:
-------------
See INSTALL for installation instructions.


Running:
--------
Type "./exobius0" to run.


Controlling:
------------
The main character can be controlled either using the keyboard :
- Cursor keys / Numpad = Movement
- Left Ctrl / Space = Shoot

or a joystick in /dev/js0 :
- Joystick = Movement
- Any button = Shoot

To proceed through storyboards, map, etc use the keypad/joypad (to change
level on the map) and either Enter, or a joystick button.

To exit back to the map from a level, press Esc.

To exit from the map and quit the game, press Esc again.


Files created:
--------------
The game will create a file in your home directory called ~/.exobius0rc
This file has scores per level separated by spaces. A score of -1 means the
level has not yet been completed.
